Source: gitkay
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Marenz <marenz@supradigital.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cargo, rustc (>= 1.75),
 libgtk-4-dev, libgraphene-1.0-dev, libssl-dev, pkg-config, cmake
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Homepage: https://github.com/Marenz/gitkay

Package: gitkay
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast, native Wayland git history viewer
 gitkay is a gitk replacement built with Rust + egui. Features a commit
 graph with colored branch lanes, syntax-highlighted diffs, file list
 sidebar, search, and Catppuccin Mocha dark theme. Starts in under 200ms.
